PrecisAmendment to the ABANDONMENT OF BRANCH LINES PROHIBITION ORDER NO. 3 which terminates the protection of a 9.85 mile portion of the CN WATERWAYS SUBDIVISION in Alberta, extending from a point at or near Lynton to a point at or near Waterways, the operation of which is no longer required as part of the basic railway network, effective November 30, 1992.

precis:
Amendment to the ABANDONMENT OF BRANCH LINES PROHIBITION ORDER NO. 3 which
terminates the protection of a 9.85 mile portion of the CN WATERWAYS
SUBDIVISION in Alberta, extending from a point at or near Lynton to a point
at or near Waterways, the operation of which is no longer required as part
of the basic railway network, effective November 30, 1992.
